data.description: Welcome to 100 Private Road 907, a large manufactured home, garage/workshop space and storage outbuilding on a large 1 acre lot in Liberty Hill.  Either rehab existing home or rear down and use this enormous lot to build your perfect home.  Terrific location close to shopping, major thoroughfares and multiple new subdivisions.  Buy for personal use or investment, either case the possibilities are endless.  Animal control, chain link fencing in front yard does not convey.
